version_description:
- minor bug fixes and improvements
- thank you for all the feedback, we're working on addressing all of it.
- please keep the reviews and feedback coming

- Fixed crashes at the start/end of levels with lots of zombies
- Fixed crashes when placing an item or explosion
- Fixed crashes mid-level when creating lots of zombies or chain reactions
- Performance and leaderboard improvements
- Additional bug fixes
- Please keep the feedback coming. We appreciate it!
